msgid ""
"You’re willing to do whatever it takes to make things right. Your mother’s massive hospital debts won’t pay themselves off, so you’ve come up with a plan: gambling. The adrenaline rush of going all in and risking everything on the mercy of the cards is also a nice perk. Lately it feels as though life has dealt you a bad hand, but you’re often able to turn terrible hands into winning ones. Who needs skill when Lady Luck is on your side?\n"
"Your game of choice is blackjack. Somehow the right cards tend to come up at the right time, and you try to hide your elation when the dealer busts yet again. You seem to go on a hot streak every night as stacks of chips grow ever taller in front of you. Such hot streaks go a long way in paying your debts, but your luck often draws the ire of both the dealer and fellow players alike. You know when to stop.\n"
"Over the years, you’ve acquired a reputation for winning that some call “cheating.” As a result, you’ve been forced to keep a low profile and gamble at a rotating list of venues. There is one venue which you revel winning at over all others: the Clover Club. Vast amounts of money are at stake every night at the speakeasy, but it’s controlled by the O’Bannion gang. Intimidating. Unscrupulous. Ruthless. No one wants to draw the attention of the gang, as your reputation surely does.\n"
"But the Clover Club has a bottom line that, above all else, must be maintained. The brazen O’Bannions are not fond of being taken advantage of, and will use any means necessary to prevent it. Here, the house always wins.\n"
"Surely that will change tonight. You pull your collar up and walk into La Bella Luna. The restaurant is virtually empty. A faint sound of bombastic music is coming from the back of the establishment. It’s clear where all the patrons are. All you can think about is getting a drink and winning big…"
msgstr ""
"你願意盡一切努力做正確的事。你母親的巨額醫療費用可不會自行解決，因此你想出了一個計劃：賭博。還能享受在卡牌賭上一切風險，梭哈時腎上腺素激增的刺激感。最近，感覺好像生活給了你滿手壞牌，但你總能扭轉滿手壞牌獲得勝利。當幸運女神站在你這邊時，誰還需要技巧？\n"
"你選擇了二十一點。不知道為什麼，你想要的牌往往會在最好的時機出現，每當莊家的點數又爆了，你都快幾乎掩飾不了自己的興高采烈。你似乎每晚都手感絕佳，桌上的籌碼越來越高，堆積如山。順風順水的手感在償還債務方面大有幫助，但這好運也常常讓莊家和其他玩家怒氣沖沖。你知道你該停手的時機。\n"
"多年以來，你已贏錢贏出了聲望，有些人甚至稱你“作弊”。因此，你不得不保持低調，並時時轉換地方賭博。有個地方：四葉草俱樂部，是你最享受的場所。每天晚上，大量的資金都在這個非法俱樂部匯聚，但這地方是歐巴尼恩幫控制的。他們恐嚇、無情、作惡多端。沒有人會想引起他們的注意，尤其是有像你這種聲望的人。\n"
"四葉草俱樂部有一個底線，無論如何都得維持這個底線。厚顏無恥的歐巴尼恩幫不喜歡被佔便宜，他們會盡一切必要手段阻止這種事發生。在這裡，莊家總是贏。\n"
"今晚，這件事肯定會改變。您拉起衣領，走進月下美人。這間餐廳看似空蕩蕩的，但建築的後面傳來微弱的音樂的轟鳴聲。很明顯所有“客人”都在哪裡。你只想趕緊喝上一杯，開始大贏四方……"

msgid "Scenario Setup"
msgstr "冒險設置"

msgid "When gathering <i>The Midnight Masks</i> encounter set, only gather the 5 treachery cards (2x False Lead and 3x Hunting Shadow). Do not gather the locations, act, agenda, and scenario reference cards from that set."
msgstr "找出<i>午夜假面</i>遭遇組時，只找出其中5張詭計卡(2張錯誤指示和3張追獵鬼影)。注意不要拿出該遭遇組中的地點、場景、密謀或冒險輔助卡。"

msgid "You may optionally decide to gather the cards included in the <i>Return to the House Always Wins</i> encounter set, as well, if your collection includes them."
msgstr "如果你的收藏中包括<i>重返百賭百勝</i>遭遇組，你可以選擇是否要加入包含在<i>重返百賭百勝</i>遭遇組的卡牌。"

msgid "If you do, perform the following additional steps:"
msgstr "如果你這麼做，依照以下的額外步驟進行："

msgid "Remove the “Return to” setup card from the game."
msgstr "將“重返”設置卡牌從遊戲中移除。"

msgid "Remove the original version of the Clover Club Lounge from the game and use the new version of the Clover Club Lounge instead."
msgstr "將原始版本的俱樂部大廳從遊戲中移除，改為使用新版本的俱樂部大廳。"

msgid "Set the Clover Club Stage aside, out of play."
msgstr "將俱樂部舞台放在一邊，位於場外。"

msgid "Include the new treachery cards with the remainder of the encounter cards."
msgstr "將新的詭計卡加入其餘的遭遇卡。"

msgid "Remember that “Skids” O’Toole has “cheated.”"
msgstr "記住“倒霉蛋”奧圖爾“作弊”了。"

msgid "Remove the original scenario reference card from <i>The House Always Wins</i> encounter set from the game. Use the new scenario reference card provided in the downloadable <i>All or Nothing</i> encounter set."
msgstr "將<i>百賭百勝</i>遭遇組中原本的冒險輔助卡牌移出遊戲。使用下載的<i>孤注一擲</i>遭遇組中提供的新冒險輔助卡牌。"

msgid "Remove the original act and agenda deck from <i>The House Always Wins</i> encounter set from the game. Build the act and agenda decks using only the new act and agenda cards provided in the downloadable <i>All or Nothing</i> encounter set."
msgstr "將<i>百賭百勝</i>遭遇組中原本的場景與密謀卡牌移出遊戲。僅用下載的<i>孤注一擲</i>遭遇組中提供的新場景與密謀卡牌構建場景和密謀牌堆。"

msgid "Remove the Peter Clover asset and the Dr. Francis Morgan story asset from the game. These cards are not used in this challenge scenario."
msgstr "將彼得·克勞佛支援卡和佛朗西斯·摩爾根博士故事支援卡從遊戲中移除。這些卡牌不會在挑戰冒險中使用。"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: each copy of the Back Hall Doorway location, each copy of the Clover Club Bouncer enemy, and the Siobhan Riley enemy."
msgstr "將下列卡牌放在一邊，位於場外：所有的走廊後門地點、所有的俱樂部保安敵人、西沃恩·萊利敵人。"

msgid "Put each of the remaining locations into play: Darkened Hall, Clover Club Lounge, Clover Club Bar, Clover Club Cardroom, and La Bella Luna."
